data.description: Your new home search ends HERE!!! Nestled on a spacious corner lot sits this darling split-level home that's move-in ready and just waiting for you! Step inside and be greeted by beautiful hardwood floors and a plethora of sunshine from all of the south facing windows. The large living area is a terrific gathering spot for family and friends. Cook up an amazing meal in the updated kitchen that features cherry stained maple cabinetry, granite counters, and stainless steel appliances. Open to the kitchen, the dining area gives everyone a view of the chef at work! Upstairs are three generous sized bedrooms all with hardwood floors, nice sized closets with double hang organization, and a nicely appointed full bath. Head to the lower level for a little playtime in the huge carpeted family room. A half bath, laundry/utility room with new washer & dryer, and access to a massive crawlspace for storage can also be found on the lower level. Enjoy easy access to the 2-car garage and have some summer fun in the fenced in back yard. New roof in 2019, new blinds in most rooms, some rooms freshly painted, and a new screen door was added this year. 2300 Mayfair Avenue is super close to Mayfair Park and Recreation Center, the primary school, and is just a short drive to Oak Brook Center, the Metra in downtown Western Springs and La Grange, and to major highways to get you wherever you need to go! Start building fantastic memories at 2300 Mayfair Avenue today! Welcome Home!
